---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Services" description="AI strategy, fractional leadership, prototyping, and independent technical review.">
  <section>
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <h1>Services</h1>
      <p class="lead mt-3">I don&rsquo;t list 15 services. I help with four kinds of problem.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="service-block">
        <h2>&ldquo;I need to figure out what to do with AI&rdquo;</h2>
        <p>For teams who&rsquo;ve been told to &ldquo;use AI&rdquo; but need honest guidance on what&rsquo;s realistic and where to start.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>AI strategy and roadmapping</li>
          <li>Discovery workshops</li>
          <li>Feasibility assessments</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="service-block">
        <h2>&ldquo;I need someone senior to lead the AI work&rdquo;</h2>
        <p>Senior expertise without the full-time hire. I embed with your team and lead the work.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fractional AI Lead / CTO</li>
          <li>Embedded technical leadership for programmes</li>
          <li>AI team building and capability assessment</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="service-block">
        <h2>&ldquo;I need something built&rdquo;</h2>
        <p>From proof of concept to production. Practical delivery, not vapourware.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>NLP and GenAI prototyping</li>
          <li>MLOps and deployment</li>
          <li>Reproducible analytical pipelines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="service-block">
        <h2>&ldquo;I need an honest outside perspective&rdquo;</h2>
        <p>Independent, no-bullshit evaluation. I&rsquo;ll tell you what&rsquo;s working and what isn&rsquo;t.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Technical due diligence</li>
          <li>Architecture and code review</li>
          <li>Vendor assessment</li>
          <li>AI ethics and governance advisory</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center">Who I work with</h2>
      <div class="grid-3 mt-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Public Sector &amp; Government</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Digital leaders and programme directors who need someone who understands procurement, governance, and the technology.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Not-for-Profits &amp; Social Impact</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Organisations with meaningful problems and limited budgets who need honest advice on what AI can realistically do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Scale-ups &amp; SMEs</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Growing companies past &ldquo;should we do AI?&rdquo; who need help with &ldquo;how?&rdquo; &mdash; without a big consultancy price tag.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Sound like your problem?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mt-2">Let&rsquo;s talk about it. 30 minutes, no obligation.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary mt-3">Book a call</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-block ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .service-block li {
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-block li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.75rem;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
